nodes.text: A serving droid in the employ of Dark Prince Xizor and the Black Sun crime syndicate once tended to a meeting between Xizor and the Hutt crime lord Jabba Desilijic Tiure within Xizor's Palace in 3.5 ABY. The serving droid presented Jabba with a tray of insectoids and vile liquids that Hutts were known to favor.
